1
00:00:00,920 --> 00:00:03,989
&gt;&gt; Salix alba variety 'Tristis',

2
00:00:03,990 --> 00:00:06,585
or weeping willow is a large tree

3
00:00:06,585 --> 00:00:09,914
with distinctively pendulous branches,

4
00:00:09,914 --> 00:00:12,044
giving its weeping characteristic.

5
00:00:12,044 --> 00:00:14,879
The buds on these branches

6
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:17,070
are smooth yellow with one scale.

7
00:00:17,070 --> 00:00:21,940
This is Salix alba 'Tristis' or Weeping willow.

